headline: 3 Industrials Stocks That Fall Short
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Unfortunately, this role also comes with a demand profile tethered to the ebbs and flows of the broader economy, and the industry is currently lagging as its six-month return of 13.6% has trailed the S&P 500’s 16.3% gain.
